    "It comprises a collection of text gathered from 45M links, totaling over 8M documents.",
    "All documents related to Wikipedia have been removed from this corpus.",
    "• Zhihu 78.",
    "The Zhihu corpus is a Chinese knowledge-sharing social platform.It enables users to ask questions, provide answers, and share knowledge, maintaining a high level of quality.",
    "Simultaneously, the platform encourages users to build social connections through interactions such as following, upvoting, commenting, and more."
